WEBVTT

1
00:00:09.801 --> 00:00:13.221
DECEMBER 2020

2
00:00:14.305 --> 00:00:16.975
JINNAM BOXING

3
00:01:26.669 --> 00:01:28.505
Oh. uh. sir.

4
00:01:28.588 --> 00:01:31.299
You need to wear a mask on the bus. sir.

5
