there are no spectators today.

180
00:11:50.626 --> 00:11:52.506
It feels rather gloomy in here.
don't you think?

181
00:11:52.545 --> 00:11:53.379
That's right.

182
00:11:53.462 --> 00:11:55.649
The Rookie of the Year tournament
