He has great showmanship.</i>

200
00:12:32.084 --> 00:12:33.335
<i>Whoa. it's a KO.</i>

201
00:12:33.878 --> 00:12:34.878
KIM RAE-HYEON
KIM GUN-WOO

202
00:12:34.920 --> 00:12:37.506
<i>We have Kim Gun-woo
going up against Kim Rae-hyeon.</i>

203
00:12:37.590 --> 00:12:40.110
<i>Kim Gun-woo in blue. everybody.
the super rookie in blue trunks.</i>

204
00:12:40.176 --> 00:12:43.554
