for a chance with his guard up.</i>

205
00:12:43.637 --> 00:12:45.598
<i>- A body blow!
- He goes to his knees!</i>

206
00:12:45.681 --> 00:12:48.184
<i>That's right.
A precision blow to the solar plexus...</i>

207
00:12:48.267 --> 00:12:50.227
